### List services
GET http://localhost:5199/services

### Create booking
POST http://localhost:5199/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "ops.manager@example.com",
  "vesselName": "MV Northern Star",
  "containerNumber": "MSCU1234567",
  "requestedDate": "2026-07-01"
}

### Add service to booking
POST http://localhost:5199/bookings/{{bookingId}}/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceItemId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "quantity": 2
}

### Submit booking
POST http://localhost:5199/bookings/{{bookingId}}/submit

### Checkout booking
POST http://localhost:5199/bookings/{{bookingId}}/checkout

### Fulfil booking
POST http://localhost:5199/bookings/{{bookingId}}/fulfil

### List recent bookings
GET http://localhost:5199/bookings
